title: Janus' New CLO ETF Starts with $100M Seed
description: Janus Henderson is launching a new ETF that will invest in bonds issued by CLOs. John Kerschner, Global Head of Securitized Products & Portfolio Manager at Janus Henderson joins "ETF IQ" to discuss. (Source: Bloomberg)
